{"tid":98264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網上流傳多份DSE試題    考評局：處理中","createTime":"2017-01-28T09:26:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T12:49:44.000Z","uid":58099,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fb2ac8f2197db88badef76826ca8338359ce77c5","tid":98264,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:26:15.000Z","msg":"［本報訊］2017年中學文憑試即將舉行，不少考生正密鑼緊鼓溫習。近日，網上流傳多份擬似今屆試卷，不少網民更聲稱已收到多份試題。今日，本報記者發現擬似流出試題的討論貼已被封鎖，不能回覆。<br />\n<br />\n考評局發言人表示，不能確定網上流傳的試題是否屬實，正緊急處理中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nFb見到<br />\n咩事？？"},{"pid":"d30b7acdaa5df0695e1bb5465fe502a4c1177d91","tid":98264,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:27:40.000Z","msg":"堅定流<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連登仔玩到咁"},{"pid":"ac238899e2ab80cb6fd036e0e28fe46fbcc31a21","tid":98264,"uid":71101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:30:47.000Z","msg":"帶起玩先嗰個連登仔會唔會比人告<br />\n有冇法律巴打解釋下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae7b92fda04bef75f0aaee1a5cd0abf4860a2e6c","tid":98264,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:31:26.000Z","msg":"咁on9玩呢d比人拉都抵死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"709662b5753d8f1c2bcc062bb288e1c287beb9a5","tid":98264,"uid":2247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:32:36.000Z","msg":"笑到仆街"},{"pid":"6fe21a2dce6acdd7362e60ea99cf1b97ea07b276","tid":98264,"uid":57646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:33:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁on9玩呢d比人拉都抵死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nOn9"},{"pid":"7d1c1489fa5d9907eed82d7d657417cdb9f42684","tid":98264,"uid":1467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-